context.name: Winchester SXP Defender FDE Pump Action Shotgun
context.excerpt: The Winchester SXP is an old favourite, the Defender FDE Pump Action Shotgun is a new and exclusive model to the SXP range.
context.content:
The Winchester SXP is an old favourite, the Defender FDE Pump Action Shotgun is a new and exclusive model to the SXP range. Produced specifically for the UK market.

Winchester SXP Defender FDE Pump Action Shotgun Features:

Calibre 12G
Barrel Length 24"
